# CODEOWNERS for Mockup OS
#
# Syntax: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-customizations/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Owners listed here are automatically requested for review on any PR that
# touches matching paths. The LAST matching rule wins, so put broad defaults
# first and sharpen for specific areas below.
#
# TODO: replace the placeholder team/handle below with the real Miko
# maintainer team once the org is set up on GitHub. Examples:
#   @miko/maintainers        — a team-level reviewer (preferred)
#   @andre-smith             — an individual handle

# Default owner for everything in the repo.
*                                           @miko/maintainers

# Core runtime — framework, shell, and app glue.
/src/mockup-os/framework/                   @miko/maintainers
/src/mockup-os/shell/                       @miko/maintainers
/src/mockup-os/app/                         @miko/maintainers

# The sidecar is security-sensitive (only file writer, handles AI calls).
# Changes here should get extra eyes.
/scripts/sidecar/                           @miko/maintainers

# Build, validate, and handoff tooling.
/scripts/build-docs.ts                      @miko/maintainers
/scripts/build-handoff.ts                   @miko/maintainers
/scripts/validate-registry.ts               @miko/maintainers

# Agent and slash-command surface. Behaviour changes here propagate to
# every session that uses Mockup OS with Claude.
/.claude/                                   @miko/maintainers
/CLAUDE.md                                  @miko/maintainers

# Community-health and governance. Treat changes as significant.
/README.md                                  @miko/maintainers
/LICENSE                                    @miko/maintainers
/CONTRIBUTING.md                            @miko/maintainers
/SECURITY.md                                @miko/maintainers
/GOVERNANCE.md                              @miko/maintainers
/ROADMAP.md                                 @miko/maintainers
/CHANGELOG.md                               @miko/maintainers
/.github/                                   @miko/maintainers

# Docs and example products can be reviewed by a broader group once
# maintainers beyond the founding set exist. For now, same owner.
/docs/                                      @miko/maintainers
/Projects/                                  @miko/maintainers
